{"tid":244492,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個大阪必食","createTime":"2017-05-15T13:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T01:55:07.000Z","uid":83761,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a66d277510b676ffae3bb97f11e77a427e1228a5","tid":244492,"uid":83761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"毒撚七月一個人去京阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇邊間啱一個人食嘅燒肉。<br />\n上網見人話松阪牛燒肉M 幾正，但歡唔歡迎一個人？有冇巴絲食過分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafe57d74944931f0ed02a15901534f3f1b8e8cb","tid":244492,"uid":10114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"架妹"},{"pid":"2d9cf461cff8fab858e19e3d395231f9475bc783","tid":244492,"uid":49344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"金龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de9282c98a6544879a9aece5b7a3d48ba5892da","tid":244492,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"金龍必食"},{"pid":"21daa0132da30f73b7afad9d8b3433ce1210240b","tid":244492,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"龜王拉麵"},{"pid":"42c9503edc910fd5c2407500aa8c3a6c1a6dfced","tid":244492,"uid":83761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>架妹</blockquote><br />\n飛田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm